# - SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL (optional)
# - DISCORD_WEBHOOK (optional)

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📝 SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 1. Copy this file:
#    cp .env.example .env

# 2. Get testnet ETH:
#    Visit: https://www.coinbase.com/faucets/base-ethereum-goerli-faucet
#    Or: https://faucet.quicknode.com/base/sepolia

# 3. Get API keys:
#    BaseScan: https://basescan.org/myapikey
#    Pinata: https://app.pinata.cloud/ (for IPFS)

# 4. Create deployment wallet:
#    - Create new MetaMask wallet
#    - Export private key (Settings > Security & Privacy > Show Private Key)
#    - Fund with ~0.1 ETH testnet
#    - NEVER use this wallet for mainnet with real funds!

# 5. Deploy contracts:
#    cd contracts
#    npm run deploy:base-sepolia

# 6. Update frontend:
#    - Copy deployed contract addresses to VITE_*_CONTRACT_ADDRESS
#    - Update neural-web3-real.js with addresses

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🔒 SECURITY BEST PRACTICES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ✅ DO:
# - Use dedicated deployment wallet with minimal funds
# - Keep private keys in password manager
# - Use hardware wallet for mainnet deployment
# - Enable 2FA on all services
# - Regularly rotate API keys
# - Use GitHub Secrets for CI/CD
# - Test on testnet first

# ❌ DON'T:
# - Commit .env to git (.env is in .gitignore)
# - Share private keys
# - Use same wallet for testnet and mainnet
# - Use personal wallet for deployment
# - Store keys in plain text files
# - Use production keys in development

